<div style="text-align: center;">
<div id="u-myDiv" style=" color:firebrick; padding: 5px 5px 5px 15px; margin-bottom:10px; border:solid 5px #068200; background:#83e27f; box-shadow: 1px 3px #888888;">
<h1 id="toc2"><span>ARBH级调查提议团“乳酪蛋糕”</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc3"><span><strong>调查主管：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3207203); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3207203&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607225409" alt="JackalRelated" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3207203)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jackalrelated" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3207203); return false;">JackalRelated</a></span></span></h2>
<h2 id="toc4"><span><strong>首席研究员：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2231487&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607225409" alt="DrMorris" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2231487)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;">DrMorris</a></span></span></h2>
<p><em>&quot;世界变成一场昆虫地狱？我们有驱虫剂来应付它。&quot;</em></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="u-myDiv" style=" padding: 5px 5px 5px 15px; margin-bottom:10px; border:dotted 1px; box-shadow: 1px 3px #888888; width: 97%;">
<p>╒═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╕</p>
<p><strong>简报：</strong>IC乳酪蛋糕的发现<br />
<strong>文字转录：</strong><br />
这里是IC“乳酪蛋糕”。这很可能是我们在基金会里最不愿意<em>做</em>的事情。但是我们已经整理了一份关于如何……好吧，世界如何走到尽头的文档。如果你愿意，你就可以在下面找到这文件。就我个人而言，我在682身上下注，但它最终证明是个饥饿的蝗虫。这是一次很好的跑团，伙计们。祝好运——你会需要它的。<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>研究员Joe Fynegan</p>
<p>╘═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╛</p>
</div>
